                        href="https://bekitzur.com/project/labor-insurance-claims-processing-system/"
                        target="_blank"
                        ) description

                    img.mob-view-imac(src="/images/utmc_imac.png" alt="")

                    .text-block.text-block_right.text-block_bottom
                        .text-block__desc
                            | Unemployment Tax Management Corporation (UTMC) is a company that handles the
